      <title>韩国总统尹永康将缺席议会开幕式 因局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/south-korea-s-yoon-to-skip-parliament-opening-as-tensions-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈将缺席国会开幕仪式，这是该国 30 多年来首位缺席国会开幕仪式的领导人，这一迹象表明党派纷争给政府实现关键政策举措的前景蒙上了阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/south-korea-s-yoon-to-skip-parliament-opening-as-tensions-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 02:56:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚总理支持率因选民面临生活成本压力而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/australian-pm-s-approval-drops-as-rba-sees-no-near-term-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯 (Anthony Albanese) 的支持率跌至他 2022 年上任以来的最低水平，因为选民报告称生活成本越来越高。与此同时，央行暗示短期内不会提供货币救济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/australian-pm-s-approval-drops-as-rba-sees-no-near-term-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 01:53:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼计划在非洲论坛期间签署 35 亿美元协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/indonesia-aims-to-sign-3-5-billion-in-deals-during-africa-forum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级外交官表示，随着全球贸易战刺激印尼寻找亚洲以外的新市场，印尼将寻求与非洲签署价值 35 亿美元的贸易和投资协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/indonesia-aims-to-sign-3-5-billion-in-deals-during-africa-forum</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:49:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工党称若维持燃油补贴将面临英镑贬值风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-risked-run-on-pound-if-fuel-subsidy-had-stayed-labour-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国下议院领袖露西·鲍威尔表示，如果财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯不取消 1000 万养老金领取者的冬季燃料补贴以填补公共财政缺口，英国将面临英镑贬值、利率上升和经济危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-risked-run-on-pound-if-fuel-subsidy-had-stayed-labour-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人质死亡事件引发抗议 以色列准备迎接劳工罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/israel-braces-for-strike-as-pressure-mounts-for-cease-fire-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列最大的劳工团体准备于周一举行全国性罢工，这是迄今为止迫使政府在加沙停火并确保被哈马斯劫持的人质释放的最强烈努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/israel-braces-for-strike-as-pressure-mounts-for-cease-fire-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 20:15:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
